Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:00.76,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1500,1065)\fs67.5}完
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個我說  我們這次文化祭是要演白雪公主對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優想要扮演什麼角色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你乘亂在吃什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:38.05,title1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,750)}「魔女與蘋果與姐姐」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:38.05,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,750)}「魔女與蘋果與姐姐」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美月會長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊是一年級的教室哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說…說的也是呢  我有點事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優說她要演魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女是王妃吧  我也想演那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼魔女會那麼有人氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這邊為什麼飛出火花了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  優就是喜歡幹些稀奇古怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡奇怪了  明明很帥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是小雫竟然會想要演魔女  真意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為仔細想了想王妃的所作所為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發現有和自己重疊的部分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和鏡子裡的自己說話很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們先試一下鏡  然後決定誰來演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊那位漂亮的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要來個蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要我要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香你冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:13:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊那位漂亮的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好入戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫  真可愛  真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個能叫可愛麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  哪個魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,更好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.74,0:13:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪邊都很微妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺到了視線…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  楓  美月會長在看這邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會是又來監視春香和優了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是想演白雪公主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是被發覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先暫時撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好歹也是學生會長  怎麼能在走廊裡奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:13:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才只是腳步跨得比較大而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼  我只是路過而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾你們了吧  再見  優
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是知道的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會長你是對白雪公主有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但又說不出口所以才在這兒轉悠的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  我真的只是路過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別再解釋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看春香同學太入迷  一不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近一直看到美月會長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,午休的時候經常像剛才那樣蹲在門後面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人竟然會幹那種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別看她那樣  或許也鼓不起勇氣來搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:15:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  為什麼琴音這種時候不上去搭話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定是太害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼小雫會覺得難過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美月會長也要來出演白雪公主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會變成那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的  騙人的  我才不演呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  這是我和你最後一次一起參加文化祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你了  就當是為了小優
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會長  你意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:16:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起偷窺  參演才能不讓人起疑地對那倆人進行監視喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  參演的話就能有更多和春香同學說話的機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我這個笨蛋  為了監視  我也加入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  美月會長說她來演白雪公主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有說來演  但是我沒說要演白雪公主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那有其它想要演的角色嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還真專一呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先看一下劇本再決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來白雪公主是個什麼故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:56.99,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,150)}簡單易懂的！白雪公主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人  最後竟然有接吻鏡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  也沒說春香同學會演白雪公主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香同學演王子的話也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香同學你演哪個角色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然小優演魔女的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就兼任王妃的侍從  王子和獵人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想演獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你更應該演其它角色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:50.04,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}張牙舞爪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不配當優的侍從
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是這個意思？
